Subject: [PATCH] fix(security): CVE-2026-42264 backport for axios 1.11.0

Backports upstream fixes for prototype pollution (GHSA-q8qp-cvcw-x6jj) and Unix socket SSRF defense (allowedSocketPaths).

Upstream commits:

- https://github.com/axios/axios/commit/47915144662f2733e6c051bdcb895a8c8f0586aa
