+# Why SNYK-JS-AXIOS-6124857 Is Already Fixed in `axios` and Requires No Patching
+
+This document explains why **SNYK-JS-AXIOS-6124857** is a **false positive** when reported against **axios v1.11.0**, and confirms that the required security fix is **already included upstream**, making any patching or backporting unnecessary.
+
+---
+
+## 📑 Table of Contents
+
+- [Overview: What Is `axios`?](#-overview-what-is-axios)
+- [Why SNYK-JS-AXIOS-6124857 Is Reported](#-why-snyk-js-axios-6124857-is-reported)
+- [Why This Issue Is Already Fixed](#-why-this-issue-is-already-fixed)
+- [Fix Lineage and Proof](#-fix-lineage-and-proof)
+- [Why This Is a False Positive](#-why-this-is-a-false-positive)
